  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Jamieson-Fausset-Brown Bible Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "6. \"Love is the fulfilling of the law\" (Ro 13:10), and the fulfilling of the law is the sure test of love.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "This is the commandment—Greek, \"The commandment is this,\" namely, love, in which all God's other commandments are summed up.",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
  },
