    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "And this is love, that we walk after his commandments,.... By observing them as a rule of conversation, in so doing love is shown to God; and such may expect the fresh discoveries of the love of God to, them; See Gill on ",
