      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "this is the commandment, that as ye have heard from the beginning,  ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "ye should walk in it; that is, this is the will of God, that his people should walk in the truth of the Gospel, and abide by it, as they heard and received it at their first conversion, from the mouths of the apostles, or other faithful ministers of the word; a reason for which, is given in 2 John 1:7. ",
